title: WATCH: Swizz Beatz vs. Just Blaze Battle One For The History Books | Honey German | Power 105.1 FM
text:
share 
Last night was one for the history books! Swizz Beatz and Just Blaze had themselves a legendary yet friendly beat battle on Instagram Live . 
During the "Battle of the Beats" we saw each super-producer going back and forth on the boards showing off what they have in their crates as well as their on-the-spot beat-making skills. 
As a treat, Swizz shared an unreleased track which features Jay Z , Nas, Jadakiss and DMX. A post shared by therealswizzz (@therealswizzz) on Feb 25, 2017 at 9:56am PST
